OL,3,CMother wants extra support for parents
OL,4,Cof children with autism
OL,6,FAntonia explains that neurodiversity
OL,7,Faffects people differently and often
OL,8,Fmakes it hard for her daughters to
OL,9,Fjoin in socially.
OL,11,FShe says: "There are no summer
OL,12,Fholidays that cater for children with
OL,13,Fneurodiversity, none.
OL,15,F"There is nowhere that you can leave
OL,16,Fyour children safely, alone, during
OL,17,Fthe summer so it's incredibly
OL,18,Fdifficult."
